This Nades will make you half invisible , but you can change it to complete invisible or 1/4 invisible by changing the output:

(...)With a parameter override of: 0-255

0 means complete invisible 255 means normal visible

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
After you throw/use the nades you will still be invisible but you can change this too by adding this Output:

My Output named:              OnPlayerUse

Target Entities named:        !activator

Via this input:               alpha

with a parameter override of: 255
